track_notes: Using bridleway track head south from the village hall car park. Track splits at SO 1234 2518. The left hand (east) side option is best and is less muddy. It took 30 mins up and 23 mins down at the end of a hard day. There is an excellent cafe / shop in nearby Talybont on Usk.
track_title: Track from village hall car park

track_notes: Start up the farm track. Keep right through gate and continue following the bridleway through a few twists and turns until it eventually meets the main bridleway along the ridge. Turn left (NW) and follow straightforwardly to the summit.
track_title: From the big layby and toilets on the A40

track_notes: Total time (including ops): 1h 20m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards.
